          </div>
        
          
        

        
      
        </figure>
      

    </div>
  


  


</div></div><div class="sqs-block html-block sqs-block-html" data-block-type="2" data-sqsp-block="text" id="block-213845a7d7383ab8ea3f"><div class="sqs-block-content">

<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content>
  <h1 style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Sabbatical Travel Blog</h1><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;"><em>‚ÄúTravel is fatal to prejudice, bigotry, and narrow-mindedness, and many of our people need it sorely on these accounts. Broad, wholesome, charitable views of men and things cannot be acquired by vegetating in one little corner of the earth all one's lifetime.‚Äù</em><br>- Mark Twain</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">In the summer of 2019, I took 3 months off to solo backpack through Southeast Asia in a bout of quarter-life crisis burnout and do my own ‚ÄòEat Pray Love self-discovery journey‚Äô üò¨. Goals included training in Muay Thai, learning about Buddhism and the roots of the mindfulness trend, and writing. I wanted to process, record, and share the lessons I learned from these formative experiences with others in a deeper way than just the highlight reel of Instagram (@plin.png). </p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">My writings since then can be found <a href="https://medium.com/@patrick-lin">on Medium</a>, here I captured my reflections after trekking in caves, meditating in forests, and eating my way through Hong Kong, Thailand, Laos, Vietnam, and Singapore!</p>
</div>




















  
  



</div></div><div class="sqs-block summary-v2-block sqs-block-summary-v2" data-block-json="&#123;&quot;hSize&quot;:null,&quot;floatDir&quot;:null,&quot;collectionId&quot;:&quot;5d1e42c2345aa60001d6074f&quot;,&quot;design&quot;:&quot;carousel&quot;,&quot;headerText&quot;:&quot;Recent Posts&quot;,&quot;textSize&quot;:&quot;medium&quot;,&quot;pageSize&quot;:10,&quot;imageAspectRatio&quot;:&quot;1.5&quot;,&quot;columnWidth&quot;:270,&quot;gutter&quot;:60,&quot;listImageSize&quot;:30,&quot;listImageAlignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;slidesPerRow&quot;:3,&quot;textAlignment&quot;:&quot;left&quot;,&quot;showTitle&quot;:true,&quot;showThumbnail&quot;:true,&quot;showExcerpt&quot;:false,&quot;showReadMoreLink&quot;:false,&quot;showPrice&quot;:true,&quot;productQuickViewEnabled&quot;:false,&quot;showPastOrUpcomingEvents&quot;:&quot;upcoming&quot;,&quot;metadataPosition&quot;:&quot;below-content&quot;,&quot;primaryMetadata&quot;:&quot;date&quot;,&quot;secondaryMetadata&quot;:&quot;none&quot;,&quot;filter&quot;:&#123;&#125;,&quot;autoCrop&quot;:true,&quot;lightbox&quot;:false,&quot;mixedContent&quot;:true,&quot;blockId&quot;:&quot;1579a78896a2ff3c3ca3&quot;&#125;" data-block-type="55" id="block-yui_3_17_2_1_1566060235861_13449"><div class="sqs-block-content">




















  
  





