<div class="sqs-html-content" data-sqsp-text-block-content>
  <p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Went to golden buddha temple, chinatown night markets, friendzone cafe, norn yaowarat</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">Felt kinda shitty about my experience thus far, decided to move hostels - lots of indecisiveness as a result of wanting to overoptimize (best location, rating, ability to socialize, etc) which often leads me to read reviews for like 2 hours and still not decide. Very happy with the place i got tho - there's no other solo travelers afaik but way cleaner, and nicer rooms.</p><p class="" style="white-space:pre-wrap;">The rigor of walking thru the entire city and plowing thru tourist sight after sight has been taking its toll - I need to shift away from the whole 'checklist' mindset of crossing as many locations as possible, and feeling fomo and regret if I didn‚Äôt get to all the 'must see events'. Hung out at a cafe (mostly for its name cuz friendzone lol) and at the hostel for awhile.</p>
